                </quote>; and</text>
						</clause>
            <clause id="HB58D9003AE4E4961934C8204777A390E">
              <enum>(ii)</enum>
              <text>by
			 inserting <quote>(except for the acquisition of radio programming)</quote>
			 before the period at the end; and</text>
						</clause>
          </subparagraph>
        </paragraph>
